description: Removes your Amazon Web Services account from the launch permissions for the specified AMI. For more information, see Cancel having an AMI shared with your Amazon Web Services account in the Amazon EC2 User Guide.

parameters.name: ImageId
parameters.description: The ID of the AMI that was shared with your Amazon Web Services account.

nested_items.name: Return
nested_items.description: Returns true if the request succeeds; otherwise, it returns an error.
